\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MediaStream/addtrack_event\"><code>addtrack</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MediaStream/removetrack_event\"><code>removetrack</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>继承</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Related pages for Media Capture and Streams</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/BlobEvent\"><code>BlobEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CanvasCaptureMediaStreamTrack\"><code>CanvasCaptureMediaStreamTrack</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/HTMLCanvasElement/captureStream\"><code>HTMLCanvasElement.captureStream()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/MediaDevices\"><code>MediaDevices</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/MediaDevices/getUserMedia\"><code>MediaDevices.getUserMedia()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/MediaStreamTrack\"><code>MediaStreamTrack</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MediaStreamTrackEvent\"><code>MediaStreamTrackEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"此页面仍未被本地化, 期待您的翻译!\"><code>MediaTrackCapabilities</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/MediaTrackConstraints\"><code>MediaTrackConstraints</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MediaTrackSettings\"><code>MediaTrackSettings</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MediaTrackSupportedConstraints\"><code>MediaTrackSupportedConstraints</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Navigator/mediaDevices\"><code>Navigator.mediaDevices</code></a></li><li><a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"此页面仍未被本地化, 期待您的翻译!\"><code>VideoStreamTrack</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>\n\n<p>The <strong><code>clone()</code></strong> method of the <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/MediaStream\"><code>MediaStream</code></a> interface creates a duplicate of the&nbsp;<code>MediaStream</code>. This new <code>MediaStream</code> object has a new unique <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/MediaStream/id\" title=\"id\"><code>id</code></a> and contains clones of every <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/MediaStreamTrack\"><code>MediaStreamTrack</code></a> contained by the <code>MediaStream</code> on which <code>clone()</code> was called.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"Syntax","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\">var <em>stream</em> = <em>MediaStream</em>.clone();</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"parameters","title":"Parameters","isH3":true,"content":"<p>None.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"return_value","title":"Return value","isH3":true,"content":"<p>A new <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/MediaStream\"><code>MediaStream</code></a> instance which has a new unique ID and contains clones of every <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/MediaStreamTrack\"><code>MediaStreamTrack</code></a> contained by the <code>MediaStream</code> on which <code>clone()</code> was called.</p>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"Specifications","id":"specifications","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://w3c.github.io/mediacapture-main/#dom-mediastream-clone","title":"Media Capture and Streams"}],"query":"api.MediaStream.clone"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Browser compatibility","id":"browser_compatibility","isH3":false,"query":"api.MediaStream.clone","dataURL":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/MediaStream/clone/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Syntax","id":"syntax"},{"text":"Specifications","id":"specifications"},{"text":"Browser compatibility","id":"browser_compatibility"}],"summary":"The clone() method of the MediaStream interface creates a duplicate of the MediaStream. This new MediaStream object has a new unique id and contains clones of every MediaStreamTrack contained by the MediaStream on which clone() was called.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"MediaStream.clone()","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"MediaStream.clone()","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/api/mediastream/clone","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/api/mediastream/clone/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web","title":"Web 开发技术"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API 接口参考"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/MediaStream","title":"媒体流 (MediaStream)"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/MediaStream/clone","title":"MediaStream.clone()"}],"pageTitle":"MediaStream.clone() - Web API 接口参考 | MDN","noIndexing":false}}